def getPrime(x):
    for i in range(2, x-1):
        if x%i == 0:
            break
    else:
        return x

listdata = [117, 119, 1113, 11113, 11119]
ret = filter(getPrime, listdata)
print(list(ret))            # [11113, 11119] ê°€ ì¶œë ¥ë¨
